🏋️ Full Body Workout & Diet Plan for 6-Pack Abs, Chest, and Biceps (No Gym)
This plan is budget-friendly, requires no gym, and focuses on building muscle and burning fat in 2-3 months.

💪 Workout Plan (6 Days a Week)
You’ll train 6 days a week, focusing on muscle growth (hypertrophy) and fat loss using bodyweight exercises.

🗓️ Weekly Schedule
Monday, Thursday – Chest & Triceps + Abs
Tuesday, Friday – Back & Biceps + Abs
Wednesday, Saturday – Legs & Shoulders + Abs
Sunday – Rest & Active Recovery
🔥 Chest, Triceps & Abs (Monday, Thursday)
Push-Ups – 4 sets of 20 reps
Incline Push-Ups (feet on a chair) – 3 sets of 15 reps
Diamond Push-Ups (triceps focus) – 3 sets of 12 reps
Dips (Use a chair/bench) – 3 sets of 12 reps
Plank – 3 sets of 45 sec
Leg Raises – 3 sets of 12 reps
Russian Twists – 3 sets of 15 reps
💪 Back, Biceps & Abs (Tuesday, Friday)
Pull-Ups (Use a bar/tree branch) – 3 sets of 8-12 reps
Chin-Ups – 3 sets of 8 reps (Biceps)
Superman Hold – 3 sets of 30 sec (Lower back)
Bodyweight Rows (Use a sturdy table) – 3 sets of 12 reps
Hanging Leg Raises – 3 sets of 10 reps
Bicycle Crunches – 3 sets of 15 reps
Side Plank (Both Sides) – 2 sets of 30 sec
🏋️ Legs, Shoulders & Abs (Wednesday, Saturday)
Squats – 4 sets of 20 reps
Jump Squats – 3 sets of 15 reps
Lunges – 3 sets of 10 reps per leg
Calf Raises – 3 sets of 20 reps
Pike Push-Ups (Shoulders) – 3 sets of 12 reps
Wall Handstand Hold – 3 sets of 30 sec
Flutter Kicks – 3 sets of 20 reps
Plank with Shoulder Tap – 3 sets of 12 reps
🔥 Cardio for Fat Loss (Daily)
Jump Rope – 10 min
Sprints – 5 rounds of 20 sec sprint + 40 sec rest
Burpees – 3 sets of 10 reps
🥗 Diet Plan for 6-Pack Abs & Muscle Growth (Budget-Friendly)
A high-protein, clean diet is essential for fat loss and muscle definition.

🔹 Morning (6-7 AM)
✅ 1 glass warm lemon water (Boosts metabolism)
✅ 5 soaked almonds & 2 walnuts
✅ 1 banana or apple

🔹 Breakfast (8-9 AM)
✅ 4 boiled eggs (or 1 bowl sprouts if vegetarian)
✅ 2 whole wheat chapatis/paratha with paneer or peanut butter
✅ 1 glass milk or homemade protein shake (banana + milk + peanut butter)

🔹 Mid-Morning Snack (11 AM)
✅ 1 handful of roasted peanuts or chana
✅ 1 seasonal fruit

🔹 Lunch (1-2 PM)
✅ 1 bowl brown rice OR 2 chapatis
✅ 1 bowl dal (lentils)
✅ 1 bowl vegetables (sabzi)
✅ 1 bowl curd/buttermilk

🔹 Evening Snack (5-6 PM)
✅ 1 glass black coffee OR green tea (for fat loss)
✅ 1 plate boiled chana, sprouts, or peanut butter toast

🔹 Dinner (8-9 PM)
✅ 1 bowl grilled paneer/chicken/fish
✅ 1 bowl steamed vegetables
✅ 1 chapati (optional)
✅ 1 bowl curd

🔹 Before Bed (10-11 PM)
✅ 1 glass warm milk with turmeric

🚀 Bonus Tips
✅ Drink 3-4 liters of water daily
✅ No sugar, junk food, or soft drinks
✅ Sleep 7-8 hours for muscle recovery
✅ Stay consistent!

In 2-3 months, you’ll see visible abs, chest, and biceps 💪🔥. Would you like a specific meal prep plan or home workout video suggestions? 🚀








